  <hr /><a name="difference"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">DIFFERENCED (or DIFFERENCING) </dt>
  <dd>1) (v) On flags, to create a variation of another flag, either by changing 
  one or more colours, or their sequence, and/or by adding or removing a charge. 
  Usually done to indicate close cultural, historical, or geographic ties � see 
  note a) below (also &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvc8.html#coreflag">core flag</a>&rsquo;, 
  &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvf2.html#flagfamily">flag family</a>&rsquo;, 
  &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dv-l.html#label">label 2)</a>&rsquo; and &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dv-t.html#templateflag">template flag</a>&rsquo;). </dd>
  <dd>2) In heraldry, see &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dv-c.html#cadency">cadency, mark of</a>&rsquo; 
  and note c) below.<br>3) See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvm1.html#marksofdifference">marks of difference 1)</a>&rsquo;
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d114.gif">
  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d114.gif" alt="[France]" border="0" height="108" /></a>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d114a.gif">
  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d114a.gif" alt="[Italy]" border="0" height="108" /></a>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d114b.gif">
  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d114b.gif" alt="[Russia]" border="0" height="108" /></a>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d4535.gif">
  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d4535.gif" alt="[Bulgaria]" border="0" height="108" /></a>
  <br />
  <em>National Flag of <a href="fr.html">France</a> (fotw); 
  National Flag of <a href="it.html">Italy</a> (fotw); 
  National flag of <a href="ru.html">Russia</a> (fotw); 
  National Flag of <a href="bg.html">Bulgaria</a></em></p>
  <p><em>Notes<br>
  a) As examples and with regard to 1), the flags of Italy and Bulgaria were 
  differenced from those of France and of Russia by changing the blue stripes to green, whilst 
  as further examples:<br>b) The flag of Slovakia was differenced from the Russian 
  tricolour by the addition of a charge, and that of Serbia by the reversal of its colour sequence
  &ndash; see &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dv-p.html#panslavic">pan-Slavic colours</a>&rsquo;.<br>
  c) Regarding 2), in heraldry the terms difference and differencing may not have exactly the same meaning, that these terms do not necessarily equate directly with cadency as shown above and that we therefore suggest a dictionary or glossary on heraldry should be consulted for further details.</em>
  </p>
	</dd>

  <hr /><a name="digitate"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">DIGITATE</dt>
  <dd>See &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvs6.html#squaretailed">square-tongued</a>&rsquo;.
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d1136.gif">
